    "description": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>微博：安格法  B站：安格法   QQ群：633659733 </li></ul><br>点击上方【添加至您的愿望单】按钮，上线后即可第一时间入手《巫族》！<br><br>《巫族》是一款单人独立开发的轻量级肉鸽自走棋游戏，讲述了奇幻世界伊塞法亚大陆的黑暗时代。策略性的组建军队，解锁英雄，善用兵种相克以及强大的组合技能。见证巫族最终的命运，并了解故事背后的真相。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343970/extras/1df38dec13d98731f178e3a7f6c88189.poster.avif?t=1680981842\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343970/extras/1df38dec13d98731f178e3a7f6c88189.webm?t=1680981842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343970/extras/1df38dec13d98731f178e3a7f6c88189.mp4?t=1680981842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>扣人心弦的剧情故事：预言之女的诞生打破了伊塞法亚长久以来的和平，战后暂由神迹之主艾米·蒂奥临时掌管巫族，如今封印之人的苏醒，巫后女儿的归来，多方势力的崛起，一切都预示着战争即将到来......</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343970/extras/54ea9b3039cbfef9c2d8d6c974084f49.poster.avif?t=1680981842\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343970/extras/54ea9b3039cbfef9c2d8d6c974084f49.webm?t=1680981842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343970/extras/54ea9b3039cbfef9c2d8d6c974084f49.mp4?t=1680981842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>手绘黑暗奇幻世界。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343970/extras/f3ccdb859ecdfe1b5a3e09784caec05b.poster.avif?t=1680981842\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/234